Fun-Fact: 
No one claims that Socialism is perfect and without problems. But we do have Data and Arguments that it's better than the current System: A System that was stress-tested by a Pandemic, which is a Thng that stress-tests Societys. 

I know of course it has Stigma pushed onto it (funny enough, we literally know who 
pushed this Stigma and it's rich, old People and big COmpanys, BUT WHATEVER, i am not 
planning to use this as a pro-socialism-argument no matter how massively telling it may be), 
so why not check out 'Second Thought', who cleans-up with Myths around it and explains the 
Data?
